summary: WFD. "When her next album gets released in March like we said long ago it would happen will you still believe in us? Can we...
question: WFD. "When her next album gets released in March like we said long ago it would happen will you still believe in us? Can we trust you or not?"
answer:
Rule Number 1 to whoever you are. Or what you’re trying to prove.

Trust No One.

I’m not here to have teams. I love Taylor, I love her talents and I used to love Karlie though and I love Kaylor, I love them being together. And that’s my view alone. I don’t know what others have.

Now, If my coding skills serve me right, we are getting candids of them before March or nearly before May.

But you know. This is not our life so anything could be change, data can be altered, situations could be changed in a blink of an eye.

So there… Well thanks for reaching out. I’m not here for games.
